            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">4%</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Trinity Study (1998)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Expected nominal return</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">7%</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">MSCI World historical average</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Expected inflation</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">2%</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">ECB target</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Capital gains tax rate</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">26%</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">D.Lgs. 461/1997</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
